### Moments of Truth

| Moment | User Emotion | Design Response |
|--------|--------------|-----------------|
| First input | "Will this work?" | Single field, instant response |
| Seeing loss | "Holy shit, that much?!" | Big number, loss framing |
| How to switch | "Ok but it's complicated..." | Step-by-step script, phone number |
| CPE confusion | "I don't know what this is" | Visual guide, "it's on your bill" |
| Future check | "I'll forget about this" | Calendar export, personal URL |

